The Mackey-Glass model.

> mackeyGlass
>   :: Floating a => Parameters a -> ((Sample a, a) -> Sample a)
> mackeyGlass p (!(V1.V1 x), !x_tau1) = V1.V1 x'
>   where
>     ! x' = beta * x_tau1 / (1 + x_tau1^10) - gamma * x
>     beta = pBeta p
>     gamma = pGamma p

